Police have increased patrols to ensure residents' safety during the World Cup. A meeting of Kisii, Migori, Nyamira, Siaya, Homa-Bay and Kisumu county commanders chaired by Nyanza Regional Police Boss Leonard Katana agreed that patrols be increased. ALSO READ:

